for scientists,

00:08:05.630 --> 00:08:07.670
probability for
engineers, probability

00:08:07.670 --> 00:08:11.440
for social scientists,
probability for astrologists.

00:08:11.440 --> 00:08:13.960
Well, what all those
books have inside

00:08:13.960 --> 00:08:16.790
them is exactly the same
models, the same equations,

00:08:16.790 --> 00:08:18.040
the same problems.

00:08:18.040 --> 00:08:21.510
They just make them somewhat
different word problems.

00:08:21.510 --> 00:08:24.780
The basic concepts are
just one and the same,

00:08:24.780 --> 00:08:28.420
